MONSUM

Usage       : cast 'monsum (value)'	: where (value) is one, two, three, ...
Accumulative: -
Duration    : (432/Intelligence of monster) hours.

   the various incarnations of this spell create monsters of the appropriate
   level to serve you as followers for a time.  The time is as long as the
   time that charm person would work on the same creature.

See Also: CREATE GOLEM, CONJURE ELEMENTAL, CHARM MONSTER, CACAODEMON
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
